[1/30] P5 English EOY Ai Tong 2025 — Q8  Primary 5  (17.4s)
============================================================
STEM: "To ___ should I address this letter?" wondered Mr Ali.
  (1) who
  (2) which
  (3) whom
  (4) whose
ANSWER: 3

ELABORATION (428 chars):
This question tests the use of **object pronouns** after a **preposition**.

The word "to" is a **preposition**, so we must use the **object pronoun** in **(3)** "whom" for the person receiving the action.

**(1)** fails because "who" is a **subject pronoun**, not an object.
**(2)** fails because "which" is used for things or animals, not people.
**(4)** fails because "whose" is a **possessive pronoun** that shows ownership.

